    "As long as sufficient data of a certain sign language can be collected for training our models, all the functionalities of our APP can be straightforwardly applied.",
    "Note that we need to train a specific sign language recognition model for each sign language.",
    "Our developed framework is thus quite general rather than restricted to a certain sign language.",
    "ConclusionIn this paper, we discuss the current communication challenges within the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community and the potential of AI technology in supporting communication for individuals with hearing loss.",
    "We showcase an inclusion-aware Auslan Learning Solution, featuring textto-sign lookup, sign-to-text translation, and an Auslan selflearning tool."
